ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
SubjectCornell, The Hon. R. Dan, RELOCATION EXPENSES
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period from April 22 to July 30, 2010, during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. R. DAN CORNELL, who was required to relocate to the City of Sudbury, Ontario, following his appointment on October 22, 2009, as a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario.
